### Get all property listings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties

### Create a new property listing
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "john@example.com",
"firstName": "John",
"lastName": "Doe",
"phone": "0712345678",
"userEmail": "john@example.com",
"userId": "user123",
"title": "Apartament modern",
"description": "Apartament cu 3 camere, renovat recent.",
"price": 90000,
"rooms": 3,
"bathrooms": 1,
"surfaceArea": 75.5,
"photoUrls": [
"https://example.com/image1.jpg",
"https://example.com/image2.jpg"
],
"photoCount": 2,
"location": {
"lat": 46.77,
"lng": 23.62
},
"address": "Str. Memorandumului 3",
"marker": {
"lat": 46.77,
"lng": 23.62
},
"amenities": ["balcony", "central heating"],
"customAmenities": ["view to the park"],
"furnished": "true",
"transactionType": "sale",
"propertyType": "apartment"
}

### Sorted by price descending
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/sorted?sort=price-high-to-low

### Sorted by price ascending
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/sorted?sort=price-low-to-high

### Sorted by newest
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/sorted?sort=newest

### No sorting (recommended)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/sorted?sort=recommended

### Get favorites for a userId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/users/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3/favorites

### Add favorite (propertyId)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/users/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3/favorites/1744310910454

### Remove favorite (propertyId)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/users/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3/favorites/1744310910454

### Check if property is favorite
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/users/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3/favorites/1744310910454/check

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/users

### Get all markers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/markers

### Get all markers posted by a user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/markers/user/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3

### Schedule a viewing
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/viewings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3",
  "propertyId": "1744310910454",
  "date": "2025-06-21",
  "time": "13:00"
}

### Submit a review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "review": "As a real estate investor, I've seen many platforms. HomeSurfers is by far the most professional and efficient.",
  "fullName": "Radu Mihai",
  "email": "radumihai@gmail.com"
}

### Submit a review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "Super!",
  "fullName": "Anonymous",
  "email": ""
}

### Submit a review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "HomeHunters made buying our first home incredibly easy. The platform is intuitive and the support team was amazing!",
  "fullName": "Maria Popescu",
  "email": "mariapopescu@gmail.com"
}

### Submit a review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "Fantastic experience! Great communication and service.",
  "fullName": "Valentina Baluță",
  "email": "valentinabaluta@gmail.com"
}

### Submit a review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "Sold my apartment in just 2 weeks! The process was transparent and I got the best price possible.",
  "fullName": "Alexandru Ionescu",
  "email": "alexandruionescu@gmail.com"
}

### Get all reviews
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews/latest

### Get average rating
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/reviews/average-rating

### Get property by userId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/user/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3

### Get recommended properties (uses FastAPI internally)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/properties/sorted?sort=recommended&userId=CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3
Accept: application/json

### Get viewings for a user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/firestore/viewings/user/CmXswKA93ddeN8xihCIUSp5ZYkF3

### Price prediction
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/calculate-price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ion",
  "lastName": "Popescu",
  "email": "ion@example.com",
  "phone": "0712345678",
  "propertyType": "apartment",
  "transactionType": "renting",
  "furnished": "furnished",
  "address": "Strada Exemplu 1",
  "rooms": 2,
  "bathrooms": 1,
  "surfaceArea": 50.0,
  "amenities": ["wifi", "air-conditioning"],
  "customAmenities": [],
  "title": "Apartament mic",
  "description": "Mic și luminos",
  "price": 0.0
}